Management.<BR>

<P>Department of Defense, DOD02: Establish a Unified Budget for the <BR>
Department of Defense; DOD03: Purchase Best Value Common Supplies <BR>
and Services; DOD06: Establish and Promote a Productivity-<BR>
Enhancing Capital Investment Fund; and DOD10: Give Department of <BR>
Defense Installation Commanders More Authority and Responsibility <BR>
over Installation Management.<BR>

<P>Department of the Interior, DOI10: Consolidate Administrative and <BR>
Programmatic Functions in DOI; and DOI11: Streamline Management <BR>
Support Systems in DOI.<BR>

<P>
