<P>2. Letter from President Clinton to The Honorable Thomas S. Foley, <BR>
Speaker of the House of Representatives, April 27, 1993.<BR>

<P>3. See McMarty, Virginia A., The President and the Budget Process: <BR>
Expanded Impoundment and Item Veto Proposals (Washington, D.C.: <BR>
