<HR>
<H2>Reengineering Through Information Technology</H2>
<p>
<p>
<p>Accompanying Report of the National Performance Review
<p>Office of the Vice President
<p>September 1993
 <p>
<HR>
 <H2>Contents</H2>
<p>
 <DL>
 <DT><A HREF="/library/reports/itexe.html">Executive Summary</A>
<p>
 <DT>Strengthen Leadership in Information Technology
<p>
 <DD><A HREF="/library/reports/it01.html">IT01:  Provide Clear, Strong Leadership to Integrate Information Technology into the Business of Government</A>
<p>
<DT>Implement Electronic Government
<p>
 <DD><A HREF="/library/reports/it02.html">IT02:  Implement Nationwide, Integrated Electronic Benefit Transfer</A>
<p>
