<P>
<P>
<P>- Alice Rivlin, OMB<BR>

<P>- Elaine Kamarck, OVP/NPR<BR>

<P>- John Koskinen, OMB<BR>

<P>- Ed DeSeve, OMB<BR>

<P>- Bob Stone, NPR<BR>

<P>- John Kamensky, NPR<BR>

<P>- Relevant OMB PADs, NPR team leads, and White House<BR>

<P>  policy council leads (see below)<BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>Note: A &quot;*&quot; indicates primary point of contact for<BR>

<P>      NPR Phase II questions<BR>

<P>
<P>
<P>
<P>
<P>
<P>
