<P>
<P>2. In a speech to federal workers at the National Academy of Sciences, August 16, 1994.<BR>

<P>3. Al Gore, <I>From Red Tape to Results:  Creating a Government that Works Better and Costs Less; Report of the National Performance Review</I> (New York:  Plume, September 1993).  The topic was expanded upon in an accompanying NPR report, <I>Improving Customer Service</I> (Washington, D.C.:  U.S. Government Printing Office, September 1993).<BR>

<P>4. National Performance Review, <I>Putting Customers First:  Standards for Serving the American People</I> (Washington, D.C.: U.S. Government Printing Office, September 1994).<BR>

<P>
