<CENTER>         BIBLIOGRAPHY<BR>
                <B>General Articles and Studies on</B><BR> 
                <B>The National Performance Review</B><BR>
                   <B>and Reinventing Government</B><BR>
                      as of September 1995<BR>
</CENTER>
<P>
<B><U>Key NPR-Generated Resources</U></B>
<P>
