Transition?," <U>PAR</U>, Nov./Dec 1992, 52:6, pp. 535-537.
<P>
Ronald C. Moe, "Rediscovering Principles of Public
Administration:  The Neglected Foundation of Public Law," <U>PAR</U>,
Mar/Apr 1995, Vol. 55, No. 2, pp. 135-146.
