James L. Sunquist, "The Concept of Government Management: Or,
What's Missing in the Gore Report," <U>PAR</U> July/August 1995, Vol.
55, No. 4, pp. 398-399.
<P>
Fred Thompson, "Matching Responsibilities with Tactics: 
Administrative Controls and Modern Government," <U>PAR</U>, July/Aug 93,
53:4, pp. 303-318.
