             <H1 align=center>Reinventing Environmental Regulation</H1>

<P><B>President Bill Clinton            </B><BR>
<B>Vice President Al Gore</B><BR>

<P>
<P>March 16, 1995<BR>


<P>                                    <B> TABLE OF CONTENTS</B><BR>

